room_title: Escape room "The Inside Job" by Headzup in Las Vegas
review: This place was AMAZING!!! We did the escape rooms and museum, ALL AROUND FUN!

room_title: Escape room "The Inside Job" by Headzup in Las Vegas
review: Headzup is an excellent place to visit whilst in Las Vegas! We completed two of their escape rooms and spent way longer than expected in their trick art museum :) Pete was excellent at helping us line up for the best photos! Thoroughly enjoyed our time here and I’m sure we’ll be back for more escape rooms next trip!
